===定價===
綠置居以市價6折發售，定價是參考2016年7月份附近20多個私人屋苑及居屋而定價，呎價平均5,658元，最平單位售價為94萬，而最貴單位售價則為298萬<ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/41636/%E7%B6%A0%E7%BD%AE%E5%B1%85%E5%AE%9A%E5%83%B9%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89-%E5%B8%82%E5%83%B9%E5%85%AD%E6%8A%9894%E8%90%AC%E5%81%9A%E6%A5%AD%E4%B8%BB-%E5%96%AE%E8%BA%AB%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB%E9%85%8D%E9%A1%8D100%E5%80%8B| title=綠置居定價曝光　市價六折94萬做業主　單身人士配額100個| newspaper=[[香港01|香港01]]| date=2016-09-06| accessdate=2016-09-06| archive-date=2017-03-05| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170305002845/http://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/41636/%E7%B6%A0%E7%BD%AE%E5%B1%85%E5%AE%9A%E5%83%B9%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89-%E5%B8%82%E5%83%B9%E5%85%AD%E6%8A%9894%E8%90%AC%E5%81%9A%E6%A5%AD%E4%B8%BB-%E5%96%AE%E8%BA%AB%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB%E9%85%8D%E9%A1%8D100%E5%80%8B| dead-url=no}}</ref>。不過價單內只得3個單位售價低於100萬元，實用面積由194至196平方呎<ref>{{cite news|author1=梁德倫|title=綠置居景泰苑下周四起揀樓　約500呎「樓王」價單曝光售近300萬|url=http://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/63927/%E7%B6%A0%E7%BD%AE%E5%B1%85%E6%99%AF%E6%B3%B0%E8%8B%91%E4%B8%8B%E5%91%A8%E5%9B%9B%E8%B5%B7%E6%8F%80%E6%A8%93-%E7%B4%84500%E5%91%8E-%E6%A8%93%E7%8E%8B-%E5%83%B9%E5%96%AE%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89%E5%94%AE%E8%BF%91300%E8%90%AC|accessdate=2017-01-05|publisher=香港01|date=2017-01-05}}</ref>。

由於景泰苑位置理想、具吸引力，揀樓場面墟冚，經過4日揀樓已賣出249個單位。不過在揀樓後出現9宗撤銷買賣協議，即「撻訂」<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://topick.hket.com/article/1692068/%E6%99%AF%E6%B3%B0%E8%8B%91%E5%86%8D%E6%9C%895%E4%BC%99%E6%92%BB%E8%A8%82%E3%80%80%E5%85%B6%E4%B8%AD2%E4%BC%99%E7%82%BA493%E5%91%8E%E5%A4%A7%E5%96%AE%E4%BD%8D |title=景泰苑再有5伙撻訂　其中2伙為493呎大單位 |accessdate=2017-03-16 |archive-date=2017-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170308133515/http://topick.hket.com/article/1692068/%E6%99%AF%E6%B3%B0%E8%8B%91%E5%86%8D%E6%9C%895%E4%BC%99%E6%92%BB%E8%A8%82%E3%80%80%E5%85%B6%E4%B8%AD2%E4%BC%99%E7%82%BA493%E5%91%8E%E5%A4%A7%E5%96%AE%E4%BD%8D |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.housingauthority.gov.hk/mini-site/gsh2016/common/pdf/transactions/transactions-king-tai.pdf |title=景泰苑的成交紀錄冊 |accessdate=2017-05-22 |archive-date=2017-03-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170329041938/http://www.housingauthority.gov.hk/mini-site/gsh2016/common/pdf/transactions/transactions-king-tai.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

